<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681171>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Bebaiotes amazonica sp. nov., female: A. Anal tube, dorsal view; B. Pygofer, posterior view; C. Gonoplac (third valvula), lateral view; D. Gonapophysis IX (second valvula), dorsal view; E. Gonapophysis VIII (first valvula), lateral view. Abbreviations: at, anal tube; dmp, dorsal margin projections; bc, bursa copulatrix; gnp, gonoplac; gnpf IX, gonapophysis IX; gnpf VIII, gonapophysis VIII; lb, lobes; lmp, lateroapical margin projections; py, pygofer. Scale bars: A–E = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681171/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681191>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Bebaiotes dorsivittata Fennah, 1947: A. Male habitus, lateral view; B. Female, habitus, lateral view; C. Male head, anterior view; D. Male head and thorax, dorsal view; E. Male abdominal process, lateral view. Scale bars: A, B= 1 mm; C, D = 0.5 mm; E = 0.3 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681191/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681193>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Bebaiotes dorsivittata Fennah, 1947, male genitalia: A. Anal tube, pygofer and gonostyli, posterior view; B. Pygofer, lateral view; C. Anal tube, dorsal view; D. Gonostyli, left lateral view; E. Gonostyli, dorsal view; F. Periandrium and inner sclerotised plates, lateral view; G. Periandrium and inner sclerotised plates, dorsal view. Scale bars: A–G = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681193/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681195>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Bebaiotes dorsivittata Fennah, 1947, female: A. Anal tube, dorsal view; B. Pygofer posterior view; C. Gonoplac (third valvula), lateral view; D. Gonapophysis IX (second valvula), dorsal view; E. Gonapophysis VIII (first valvula), lateral view. Scale bars: A–E = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681195/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681241>
    dc:description "FIGURE 37. Antennae of Bebaiotes species. A. Bebaiotes amazonica sp. nov.; B. Bebaiotes banksi (Metcalf, 1938); C. Bebaiotes bia sp. nov.; D. Bebaiotes dichromata sp. nov.; E. Bebaiotes dorsivittata Fennah, 1947; F. Bebaiotes guianesus (Fennah, 1947). Abbreviations: de, cuticular denticles; fb, flagellar base; m, microtrichia; pe, pedicel; pi, plaque organs. Scale bars: A, B, E, F = 100 μm; C = 200 μm; D = 50μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681241/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681249>
    dc:description "FIGURE 40. Wings of Bebaiotes species. A. Bebaiotes dorsivittata Fennah, 1947, forewing; B. Bebaiotes dorsivittata Fennah, 1947, hind wing; C. Bebaiotes guianesus (Fennah, 1947), forewing; D. Bebaiotes guianesus (Fennah, 1947), hind wing; E. Bebaiotes macroptera sp. nov., forewing; F. Bebaiotes macroptera sp. nov., hind wing; G. Bebaiotes parallela sp. nov., forewing; H. Bebaiotes parallela sp. nov., hind wing. Scale bars: A–H = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681249/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681255>
    dc:description "FIGURE 43. Geographical distribution of Bebaiotes species. Bebaiotes banksi (Metcalf, 1938); Bebaiotes dorsivittata Fennah, 1947; Bebaiotes guianesus (Fennah, 1947); Bebaiotes parallela sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10681255/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

